Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 07:28:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] DMs: apply the "private counsel" Bruinen register + finish
 prototype deltas
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Brings the live Direct Messages surface up to the design handoff
(design_handoff_dm_reimagine) now that its structure/backend already
landed on main. Visual + small template deltas only — no routes,
controllers, DB, CSRF, or feature gates change.

- app.css: add a cool river `--dm-*` register scoped to `.dm-shell` and
  repoint the DM panes + every status signal (active row, unread dot,
  unread time, search focus, receipt check, reference rule, filter
  chips) to river. Gold stays "my voice"/esteem; green stays actions.
- Lock signatures: river lock eyebrow on the list + conversation headers
  (Private counsel / Private group) and an opening "Private — only those
  named here can read" divider.
- Rank pill (gold "Owner") beside a group author, from conversation role.
- Quoted-reply blockquote (gold rule, italic) for message markdown quotes.
- Composer -> calm river pill-well with a round send button. Keeps
  class="composer" so composer.js (toolbar/drafts) and the user's
  enter_to_send preference are untouched; the pill is robust to the
  injected toolbar/counter (verified against a rendered harness).
- icon.php: add the Lucide "lock" mark.
- sidebar.php: keep "Messages" active on /messages/{id} (prefix match).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_014ArR3LfGjE8pyVZnwY7hwf
